<paragraph id="020230DDAAA7C69B9AD182058C6EA27B" pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Introduced to the FSA region and found in Namibia and the Western Cape Province of South Africa. Native to the Mediterranean Sea region of Europe, North Africa and western Asia.</paragraph>
